Finger Print scanner: 


    Red: Depending on the accepted voltage of the sensor (3.3V or 5V).
    White: RXD
    Green: TXD
    Black: GND


	ls /dev/ttyUSB* // check is sensor detected
	
	Installation of the Raspberry Pi Fingerprint Library: 
	1)	sudo bash
	2)	// download packages and library // alternitivly https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-Fingerprint-Sensor-Library -> https://github.com/bastianraschke/pyfingerprint
		wget -O - http://apt.pm-codeworks.de/pm-codeworks.de.gpg | apt-key add -
		wget http://apt.pm-codeworks.de/pm-codeworks.list -P /etc/apt/source
		
	3) 	// update packages and install pyton library
		apt-get update
		apt-get install python-fingerprint --yes 
		
		
